Whether to tell Chii-chan what Kanazawa told me or not.[l][r]
[r]Whether to turn our backs on this world or cling to it.[l][r]
Whether to do whatever my beloved Chii-chan wants,[r]
or... something else.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

